{"tid":887711,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣成日會好易比人誤會？","createTime":"2018-11-03T06:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T04:31:44.000Z","uid":219889,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"98c17b08a257d142eae40cc668f4206157a2f2e6","tid":887711,"uid":219889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T06:30:29.000Z","msg":"但通常仲會唔會浪費時間去解釋？<br />\n比人誤會就好似點解釋都好無力咁<br />\n但其實比人誤會到底係自己問題定係人地問題<br />\n係你 你點揀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBy一個成日要解釋而心累嘅人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3562c2811d3f1f1380d8412f75a64411c8897660","tid":887711,"uid":219889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T06:40:02.000Z","msg":"想唔理又唔想唔解釋食死貓 一方面又心酸在點解作為你朋友但要誤會你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5419d8846af615a05e7ed927bf9b8d1c7eabb758","tid":887711,"uid":109655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T06:43:41.000Z","msg":"誤會咩先 意思好廣泛喎"},{"pid":"00915abcb74c2e8b7a9fd78b68c4968fb5025a0a","tid":887711,"uid":219889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5419d8846af615a05e7ed927bf9b8d1c7eabb758","tid":887711,"uid":109655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T06:43:41.000Z","msg":"誤會咩先 意思好廣泛喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T06:47:03.000Z","msg":"咩誤會都係啦 有時吹水講笑都會比人誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比人強加意思呀 又會有時誤會我份人性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講一句就比人加上十萬種語氣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4b4ecc133cf1c281f8172afad06e62616b6e32","tid":887711,"uid":165024,"like":